TY  - JOUR
T1  - Note: An Improvement to the Dynamic Cycle Lengths Heuristic for Scheduling the Multi-Item, Single-Machine
AU  - Leachman, Robert C.
AU  - Xiong, Zhong K.
AU  - Gascon, André
AU  - Park, Kwangtae
Y1  - 1991/09/01
PY  - 1991
DA  - 1991/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.37.9.1201
